= FFII Board candidate: Felipe Wersen =

''Felipe Wersen is a candidate for a position in the FFII board.''

Felipe Wersen is a calm, logically acting type of person. He has a deep insight on a lot of FFII's activities, and has already helped to improve the organizational structures of FFII more than one time during the Software Patent campaign.

Felipe is capable of assessing when a regulation is appropriate for a certain aim and when it isn't.

